ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAddition to Richibucto Indian Reserve No. 15, New Brunswick
PrecisOrder setting apart 214.1 hectares (528.7 acres) of land, excluding mines and minerals, for the use and benefit of the Elsipogtog First Nation as an addition to RICHIBUCTO INDIAN RESERVE No. 15, located in the Local Service District of Weldford, Kent County, approximately 12 kilometres from Rexton, in New Brunswick.
